Follow these steps to set up and build your Next.js website:

Initialize the Project: Create a Next.js project using JavaScript.
Set Up Tailwind CSS: Install and configure Tailwind CSS for styling.
Add Shadcn UI: Use the Shadcn UI CLI to integrate accessible components.
Add React Bits: Install React Bits for animated components, following its documentation.
Build and Test: Create pages and components based on your MVP document, ensuring responsiveness and accessibility, then test and deploy.